<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-03-1062 </DOCNO><TEXT>This patent describes a process for preparing a glass or glass-ceramicto metal seal comprising contacting the glass with the metal and heat-treatingthe glass and metal under conditions whereby the glass to metal sealis effected and, optionally, the glass is converted to a glass-ceramic.The improvement comprises carrying out the heat-treating step under hotisostatic pressing and using molten glass.</TEXT></DOC>